@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Erişim Engellendi</title>
    <link href="~/assets/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #d65d5d;
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #777;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

            .btn-home:hover {
                background-color: #d65d5d;
                color: white;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-card">
        <h1>403</h1>
        <h3>Giriş Yetkiniz Yok!</h3>
        <p>Üzgünüz, bu sayfaya erişim yetkiniz bulunmuyor. Burası sadece yetkili personele (Admin) özeldir.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Anasayfaya Dön</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
